%%{init: {"sequence": {"mirrorActors": false}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor UserA as User A
    actor UserB as User B
    participant Dashboard as Shared Dashboard
    participant API as Contextual API (/api/...)
    participant DB as Supabase DB
    participant RT as Supabase Realtime

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
    UserA->>Dashboard: Type "Check the logs" in Chat
    Dashboard->>API: POST /api/messages {content, project_id}
    API->>DB: INSERT INTO messages
    DB-->>RT: New Row event
    RT-->>UserB: Broadcast message
    UserB-->>Dashboard: UI re-renders chat bubble
    end

    rect rgb(248, 240, 255)
    UserA->>Dashboard: Publish Feedback Form
    Dashboard->>API: POST /api/forms {title, json_fields}
    API->>DB: INSERT INTO forms
    DB-->>RT: New Row
    RT-->>UserB: "Notification: New Form Available"
    UserB->>Dashboard: Opens Form Filler
    Dashboard->>API: POST /api/form-responses {answers}
    API->>DB: INSERT INTO form_responses
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
    UserA->>Dashboard: Add Repo "TaskFlow-Engine"
    Dashboard->>API: POST /api/repo-links {url, owner, repo}
    API->>API: Verify URL accessibility (HEAD request)
    API->>DB: INSERT INTO repo_links
    API-->>Dashboard: 201 Created
    Dashboard->>Dashboard: Render GitHub Card with link
    end
